{
  "stem": "280.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's when I saw my mother the last time, at the railway station in Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father didn't want to board the-- the-- the-- the train, and they pushed him to, because he was screaming, [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he sent me that I should look for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I couldn't-- I couldn't find her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So one sister and myself and my father went into another-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] car, in the railway car, and the rest of the family were in the other.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that, you know, I-- I didn't think of anything else, where we are going or what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I just thinking that I'm separated from my mother, and my father is crying there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The trip to Auschwitz, because that's where we were-- that's what the destination was-- of course, we didn't know where-- took two days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we arrived in Auschwitz the day after-- after [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where we keep the yahrzeit, the first day after [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For my parents and the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so I told you it was a trip of two days--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and two nights.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In these boxcars, little windows which had iron rods on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I managed to get to the window, and there were peasants-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] peasants outside, you know, by the railway car.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And instead that they should give us something, I ask them, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they screamed back in Hungarian, to your death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I took back-- I didn't tell anything to my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I thought that's antisemitism, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't think that they know anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
